casebody.data:
No. 11A117. Florida, Applicant v. Manuel Valle. 564 U.S. 1057, 132 S. Ct. 54,

180 L. Ed. 2d 922,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 5082. July 29, 2011.

Application to vacate the stay of execution of sentence of death entered by the Florida Supreme Court on July 25, 2011, presented to Justice Thomas, and by him referred to the Court, denied.
